 (not a political propagandist) who would be allowed to comment freely on the historical myth created in Moscow.

We are leaving for Genoa tomorrow morning. We shall be on Saturday at the Hotel Colombia-Excelsior, Genoa.





Sincerely,

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: MORRIS BISHOP

TLS, 1 p. Mrs. Morris Bishop.





Genoa

December 7, 1959

